{
  "video_id": "R5bn9EvOQVg",
  "title": "Charles Hazlewood: Trusting the ensemble",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "I am a conductor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "to talk to you about trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "My job depends upon it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "There has to be, between me and the orchestra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "an unshakable bond of trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "born out of mutual respect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "through which we can spin a musical narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "that we all believe in."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "Now in the old days, conducting, music making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "was less about trust and more, frankly, about coercion."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "Up to and around about the Second World War,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "conductors were invariably dictators --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "these tyrannical figures"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "who would rehearse, not just the orchestra as a whole, but individuals within it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "within an inch of their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m happy to say now that the world has moved on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "music has moved on with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "We now have a more democratic view and way of making music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "a two-way street."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "I, as the conductor, have to come to the rehearsal with a cast-iron sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "of the outer architecture of that music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "within which there is then immense personal freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "for the members of the orchestra to shine."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "For myself, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "I have to completely trust my body language."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all I have at the point of sale."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s silent gesture."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "I can hardly bark out instructions while we&#39;re playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, the Scottish Ensemble."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "So in order for all this to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "obviously I have got to be in a position of trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "I have to trust the orchestra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "and, even more crucially, I have to trust myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "Think about it: when you&#39;re in a position of not trusting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "You overcompensate."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "And in my game, that means you overgesticulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "You end up like some kind of rabid windmill."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "And the bigger your gesture gets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "the more ill-defined, blurry"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "and, frankly, useless it is to the orchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "You become a figure of fun. There&#39;s no trust anymore, only ridicule."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "And I remember at the beginning of my career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "again and again, on these dismal outings with orchestras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "I would be going completely insane on the podium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "trying to engender a small scale crescendo really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "just a little upsurge in volume."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "Bugger me, they wouldn&#39;t give it to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time in those early years"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "weeping silently in dressing rooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "And how futile seemed the words of advice to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "from great British veteran conductor Sir Colin Davis"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "who said, \"Conducting, Charles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "is like holding a small bird in your hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "If you hold it too tightly, you crush it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "If you hold it too loosely, it flies away.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "I have to say, in those days, I couldn&#39;t really even find the bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "Now a fundamental"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "and really viscerally important experience for me, in terms of music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "has been my adventures in South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "the most dizzyingly musical country on the planet in my view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "but a country which, through its musical culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "has taught me one fundamental lesson:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "that through music making"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "can come deep levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "of fundamental life-giving trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "Back in 2000, I had the opportunity to go to South Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "to form a new opera company."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "So I went out there, and I auditioned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "mainly in rural township locations, right around the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "I heard about 2,000 singers"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "and pulled together a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "of 40 of the most jaw-droppingly amazing young performers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "the majority of whom were black,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "but there were a handful of white performers."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "Now it emerged early on in the first rehearsal period"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "that one of those white performers"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "had, in his previous incarnation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "been a member of the South African police force."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "And in the last years of the old regime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "he would routinely be detailed to go into the township"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "to aggress the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "Now you can imagine what this knowledge did to the temperature in the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "the general atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s be under no illusions."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "In South Africa, the relationship most devoid of trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "is that between a white policeman"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "and the black community."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "So how do we recover from that, ladies and gentlemen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "Simply through singing."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "We sang, we sang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "we sang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "and amazingly new trust grew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "and indeed friendship blossomed."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "And that showed me such a fundamental truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "that music making and other forms of creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "can so often go to places"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "where mere words cannot."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "So we got some shows off the ground. We started touring them internationally."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "One of them was \"Carmen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "We then thought we&#39;d make a movie of \"Carmen,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "which we recorded and shot outside on location"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "in the township outside Cape Town called Khayelitsha."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "The piece was sung entirely in Xhosa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "which is a beautifully musical language, if you don&#39;t know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"U-Carmen e-Khayelitsha\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "literally \"Carmen of Khayelitsha.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "I want to play you a tiny clip of it now"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "for no other reason than to give you proof positive"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "that there is nothing tiny about South African music making."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "Something which I find utterly enchanting"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "about South African music making"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s so free."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "South Africans just make music really freely."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 453260.0,
      "text": "And I think, in no small way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 453260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s due to one fundamental fact:"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not bound to a system of notation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t read music."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "They trust their ears."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "You can teach a bunch of South Africans a tune in about five seconds flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "And then, as if by magic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "they will spontaneously improvise a load of harmony around that tune"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "because they can."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "Now those of us that live in the West, if I can use that term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "I think have a much more hidebound attitude or sense of music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 477260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "that somehow it&#39;s all about skill and systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "Therefore it&#39;s the exclusive preserve"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "of an elite, talented body."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "And yet, ladies and gentlemen, every single one of us on this planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "probably engages with music on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "And if I can broaden this out for a second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m willing to bet that every single one of you sitting in this room"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "would be happy to speak with acuity, with total confidence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "about movies, probably about literature."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "But how many of you would be able to make a confident assertion"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "about a piece of classical music?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "Why is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "And what I&#39;m going to say to you now"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "is I&#39;m just urging you to get over"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "this supreme lack of self-confidence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 518260.0,
      "text": "to take the plunge, to believe that you can trust your ears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "you can hear some of the fundamental muscle tissue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "fiber, DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "what makes a great piece of music great."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got a little experiment I want to try with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "Did you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "that TED is a tune?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "A very simple tune based on three notes -- T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "Now hang on a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "I know you&#39;re going to say to me, \"T doesn&#39;t exist in music.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 539260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "Well ladies and gentlemen, there&#39;s a time-honored system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "which composers have been using for hundreds of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "which proves actually that it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "If I sing you a musical scale: A, B, C, D, E, F, G --"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "and I just carry on with the next set of letters in the alphabet, same scale:"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "H, I, J, K, L, M, N,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "O, P, Q, R, S, T -- there you go."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "T, see it&#39;s the same as F in music."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "So T is F."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 564260.0,
      "text": "So T, E, D is the same as F, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 564260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "Now that piece of music that we played at the start of this session"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "had enshrined in its heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 571260.0,
      "text": "the theme, which is TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 571260.0,
      "end_time": 573260.0,
      "text": "Have a listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "Do you hear it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "Or do I smell some doubt in the room?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "Okay, we&#39;ll play it for you again now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to highlight, we&#39;re going to poke out the T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ll pardon the expression."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "Oh my goodness me, there it was loud and clear, surely."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "I think we should make this even more explicit."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, it&#39;s nearly time for tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "Would you reckon you need to sing for your tea, I think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "I think we need to sing for our tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 613260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to sing those three wonderful notes: T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 613260.0,
      "end_time": 615260.0,
      "text": "Will you have a go for me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "Audience: T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "Charles Hazlewood: Yeah, you sound a bit more like cows really than human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 622260.0,
      "text": "Shall we try that one again?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 622260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "And look, if you&#39;re adventurous, you go up the octave."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 626260.0,
      "text": "T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 626260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "Audience: T, E, D."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "CH: Once more with vim. (Audience: T, E, D.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "There I am like a bloody windmill again, you see."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 636260.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re going to put that in the context of the music."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 636260.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "The music will start, and then at a signal from me, you will sing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "One more time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "with feeling, ladies and gentlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "You won&#39;t make the key otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 662260.0,
      "text": "Well done, ladies and gentlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 662260.0,
      "end_time": 665260.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t a bad debut for the TED choir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 665260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "not a bad debut at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s a project that I&#39;m initiating at the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672260.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m very excited about and wanted to share with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 674260.0,
      "text": "because it is all about changing perceptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 674260.0,
      "end_time": 677260.0,
      "text": "and, indeed, building a new level of trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 677260.0,
      "end_time": 680260.0,
      "text": "The youngest of my children was born with cerebral palsy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 680260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "which as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 682260.0,
      "end_time": 684260.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t have an experience of it yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 684260.0,
      "end_time": 686260.0,
      "text": "is quite a big thing to take on board."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 686260.0,
      "end_time": 689260.0,
      "text": "But the gift that my gorgeous daughter has given me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 689260.0,
      "end_time": 691260.0,
      "text": "aside from her very existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 691260.0,
      "end_time": 694260.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s opened my eyes to a whole stretch of the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 694260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "that was hitherto hidden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 698260.0,
      "text": "the community of disabled people."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 698260.0,
      "end_time": 701260.0,
      "text": "And I found myself looking at the Paralympics and thinking how incredible"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 701260.0,
      "end_time": 704260.0,
      "text": "how technology&#39;s been harnessed to prove beyond doubt"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 706260.0,
      "text": "that disability is no barrier"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "to the highest levels of sporting achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "Of course there&#39;s a grimmer side to that truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "which is that it&#39;s actually taken decades for the world at large"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "to come to a position of trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 719260.0,
      "text": "to really believe that disability and sports can go together"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 719260.0,
      "end_time": 722260.0,
      "text": "in a convincing and interesting fashion."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 722260.0,
      "end_time": 724260.0,
      "text": "So I find myself asking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 724260.0,
      "end_time": 726260.0,
      "text": "where is music in all of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 726260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t tell me that there aren&#39;t millions of disabled people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 728260.0,
      "end_time": 730260.0,
      "text": "in the U.K. alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 730260.0,
      "end_time": 733260.0,
      "text": "with massive musical potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 733260.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "So I decided to create a platform for that potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 736260.0,
      "end_time": 738260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to be Britain&#39;s first ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738260.0,
      "end_time": 740260.0,
      "text": "national disabled orchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 740260.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called Paraorchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 744260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show you a clip now"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "of the very first improvisation session that we had."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 746260.0,
      "end_time": 748260.0,
      "text": "It was a really extraordinary moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 748260.0,
      "end_time": 751260.0,
      "text": "Just me and four astonishingly gifted disabled musicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 751260.0,
      "end_time": 754260.0,
      "text": "Normally when you improvise --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 754260.0,
      "end_time": 756260.0,
      "text": "and I do it all the time around the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 756260.0,
      "end_time": 758260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s this initial period of horror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 758260.0,
      "end_time": 760260.0,
      "text": "like everyone&#39;s too frightened to throw the hat into the ring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 760260.0,
      "end_time": 762260.0,
      "text": "an awful pregnant silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 762260.0,
      "end_time": 764260.0,
      "text": "Then suddenly, as if by magic, bang! We&#39;re all in there"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 764260.0,
      "end_time": 766260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s complete bedlam. You can&#39;t hear anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 766260.0,
      "end_time": 768260.0,
      "text": "No one&#39;s listening. No one&#39;s trusting."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 768260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "No one&#39;s responding to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 771260.0,
      "end_time": 773260.0,
      "text": "Now in this room with these four disabled musicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 773260.0,
      "end_time": 775260.0,
      "text": "within five minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 775260.0,
      "end_time": 777260.0,
      "text": "a rapt listening, a rapt response"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 777260.0,
      "end_time": 780260.0,
      "text": "and some really insanely beautiful music."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 782260.0,
      "end_time": 790260.0,
      "text": "(Video) (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 790260.0,
      "end_time": 792260.0,
      "text": "Nicholas:: My name&#39;s Nicholas McCarthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 792260.0,
      "end_time": 794260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m 22, and I&#39;m a left-handed pianist."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 794260.0,
      "end_time": 797260.0,
      "text": "And I was born without my left hand -- right hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 797260.0,
      "end_time": 800260.0,
      "text": "Can I do that one again?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 800260.0,
      "end_time": 807260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 807260.0,
      "end_time": 809260.0,
      "text": "Lyn: When I&#39;m making music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 809260.0,
      "end_time": 812260.0,
      "text": "I feel like a pilot in the cockpit flying an airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 812260.0,
      "end_time": 814260.0,
      "text": "I become alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 814260.0,
      "end_time": 825260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 825260.0,
      "end_time": 828260.0,
      "text": "Clarence: I would rather be able to play an instrument again"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 828260.0,
      "end_time": 830260.0,
      "text": "than walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 830260.0,
      "end_time": 832260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s so much joy and things"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 832260.0,
      "end_time": 836260.0,
      "text": "I could get from playing an instrument and performing."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 836260.0,
      "end_time": 840260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s removed some of my paralysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 840260.0,
      "end_time": 855260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 855260.0,
      "end_time": 862260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 862260.0,
      "end_time": 865260.0,
      "text": "CH: I only wish that some of those musicians were here with us today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 865260.0,
      "end_time": 868260.0,
      "text": "so you could see at firsthand how utterly extraordinary they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 868260.0,
      "end_time": 870260.0,
      "text": "Paraorchestra is the name of that project."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 870260.0,
      "end_time": 872260.0,
      "text": "If any of you thinks you want to help me in any way"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 872260.0,
      "end_time": 875260.0,
      "text": "to achieve what is a fairly impossible and implausible dream still at this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 875260.0,
      "end_time": 877260.0,
      "text": "please let me know."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 877260.0,
      "end_time": 879260.0,
      "text": "Now my parting shot"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 879260.0,
      "end_time": 881260.0,
      "text": "comes courtesy of the great Joseph Haydn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 881260.0,
      "end_time": 884260.0,
      "text": "wonderful Austrian composer in the second half of the 18th century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 884260.0,
      "end_time": 886260.0,
      "text": "spent the bulk of his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 886260.0,
      "end_time": 889260.0,
      "text": "in the employ of Prince Nikolaus Esterhazy, along with his orchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 889260.0,
      "end_time": 892260.0,
      "text": "Now this prince loved his music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 892260.0,
      "end_time": 895260.0,
      "text": "but he also loved the country castle that he tended to reside in most of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 895260.0,
      "end_time": 897260.0,
      "text": "which is just on the Austro-Hungarian border,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 897260.0,
      "end_time": 899260.0,
      "text": "a place called Esterhazy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 899260.0,
      "end_time": 901260.0,
      "text": "a long way from the big city of Vienna."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 901260.0,
      "end_time": 903260.0,
      "text": "Now one day in 1772,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 903260.0,
      "end_time": 905260.0,
      "text": "the prince decreed that the musicians&#39; families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 905260.0,
      "end_time": 907260.0,
      "text": "the orchestral musicians&#39; families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 907260.0,
      "end_time": 909260.0,
      "text": "were no longer welcome in the castle."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 909260.0,
      "end_time": 912260.0,
      "text": "They weren&#39;t allowed to stay there anymore; they had to be returned to Vienna --"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 912260.0,
      "end_time": 915260.0,
      "text": "as I say, an unfeasibly long way away in those days."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 915260.0,
      "end_time": 919260.0,
      "text": "You can imagine, the musicians were disconsolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 919260.0,
      "end_time": 922260.0,
      "text": "Haydn remonstrated with the prince, but to no avail."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 922260.0,
      "end_time": 924260.0,
      "text": "So given the prince loved his music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 924260.0,
      "end_time": 927260.0,
      "text": "Haydn thought he&#39;d write a symphony to make the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 927260.0,
      "end_time": 930260.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re going to play just the very tail end of this symphony now."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 930260.0,
      "end_time": 933260.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;ll see the orchestra in a kind of sullen revolt."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 933260.0,
      "end_time": 935260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pleased to say, the prince did take the tip"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 935260.0,
      "end_time": 937260.0,
      "text": "from the orchestral performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 937260.0,
      "end_time": 939260.0,
      "text": "and the musicians were reunited with their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 939260.0,
      "end_time": 942260.0,
      "text": "But I think it sums up my talk rather well, this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 942260.0,
      "end_time": 944260.0,
      "text": "that where there is trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 944260.0,
      "end_time": 947260.0,
      "text": "there is music -- by extension life."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 947260.0,
      "end_time": 949260.0,
      "text": "Where there is no trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 949260.0,
      "end_time": 952260.0,
      "text": "the music quite simply withers away."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 956260.0,
      "end_time": 966260.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1146260.0,
      "end_time": 1169260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}